    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it does make sense, but it's also terrifying. i feel like i'm just performing the role of a human. going to work, eating, sleeping... but there's no pilot in the cockpit. there's no \"me\" left to find. if the soul of the artist is what made life worth living, and that's dead... then what am i even doing? what's the point of maintaining this vessel if the person who was supposed to inhabit it has already left?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
